'''赵骏'''（{{bd|1986年|12月12日}}），[[山东|山东]][[济南|济南]]人，中国[[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手、[[国际象棋特级大师|特级大师]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chess.sport.org.cn/danzhou/qs/2010-06-03/2026935.html|title=海南儋州首届特级大师超霸战十强巡礼：赵 骏|date=2010-06-03|work=中国棋院在线|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120403043442/http://chess.sport.org.cn/danzhou/qs/2010-06-03/2026935.html|archivedate=2012-04-03}}</ref>

==生平==
2004年，17岁的赵骏获得[[国际象棋特级大师|国际象棋特级大师]]称号。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fide.com/index.php?option=com_fidetitles&view=appsdt&cat=0&per=7&aid=8602522 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120603173804/http://www.fide.com/index.php?option=com_fidetitles&view=appsdt&cat=0&per=7&aid=8602522 |archivedate=2012-06-03 }}</ref>2015年1月，他以8/9的优异成绩获得黑斯廷斯国际象棋公开赛冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.chessbase.com/post/zhao-jun-bulldozes-hastings-chess-congress|title=Zhao Jun bulldozes Hastings Chess Congress|publisher=ChessBase|author=Priyadarshan Banjan|date=7 January 2015|accessdate=11 September 2015|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120174500/https://en.chessbase.com/post/zhao-jun-bulldozes-hastings-chess-congress|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/chess/11334972/Zhao-Jun-conquers-Hastings-Chinese-grandmaster-wins-worlds-oldest-chess-congress.html|title=Zhao Jun conquers Hastings: Chinese grandmaster wins world's oldest chess congress|publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]]|last=Pein|first=Malcolm|authorlink=Malcolm Pein|date=9 January 2015|accessdate=11 September 2015|archive-date=2020-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523062826/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/chess/11334972/Zhao-Jun-conquers-Hastings-Chinese-grandmaster-wins-worlds-oldest-chess-congress.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

